<i>noun</i>: 희비극 [히비극] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>희비극 [히비극]</dt><br>
<dd>1. comedy and tragedy</dd><br>
<dd>희극과 비극.</dd><br>
<dd>A compound noun for comedy and tragedy.</dd><br>
<dd>2. tragicomedy</dd><br>
<dd>희극적인 요소와 비극적인 요소가 섞여 있는 연극.</dd><br>
<dd>A genre of theater that combines comical and tragic elements.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>